These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Music-Genre: hip-hop, electronic, trance, disco
Pet: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. Pet:mouse is on the left of Music-Genre:trance##1
2. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the left of Pet:goat##1
3. Music-Genre:disco is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:horse is on the left or right of Pet:mouse##3
5. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | electronic | disco | trance |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
City: prague, venice, boston, london
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. City:prague is on the left of City:boston##1
3. City:boston is in an odd position##4
4. City:prague == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. City:venice is on the right of City:boston##1
6. City:prague == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| City   | london    | prague | boston | venice    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Beverage: soy-milk, iced-tea, 7up, sprite
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Beverage:sprite is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Beverage:7up is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Beverage:iced-tea##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Beverage:iced-tea is on the right of Beverage:7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage          | sprite | 7up | iced-tea    | soy-milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

