3. Beverage:coffee is in an odd position##4
4. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left of Beverage:7up##1
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Hobby:cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Beverage   | coffee       | milk   | hot-chocolate    | 7up  |

