.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Job: coach, librarian, entrepreneur, journalist
Music-Genre: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. Job:coach == Music-Genre:jazz##1
2. Music-Genre:disco is on the right of Job:coach##1
3. Music-Genre:jazz is between Music-Genre:disco and Job:entrepreneur##2
4. Job:coach is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:jazz is on the left or right of Music-Genre:disco##3
6. Job:librarian is on the left or right of Music-Genre:dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Job      | librarian       | entrepreneur   | coach | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

