3. Transport:van is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:strawberry##1
5. Food:strawberry is on the right of Transport:car##1
6. Food:pepper is in an even position##4
7. Food:corn == Transport:jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Transport   | van | car    | bike       | jet-ski |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

